            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"higlass-index-explorer\">HiGlass index explorer</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Renders the bundled <code>higlass_index_viewconf.json</code> (TCGA bulk multivec\ntracks hosted on resgen.io) with <code>higlass-python</code>. The view config ships\nas package data inside <code>epifolio</code>, so no network fetch is needed beyond\nthe HiGlass tile servers referenced by the tracks.</span></span>"
